Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Defending Kingsley Amis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xjfl
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Feb 1985
Defending Kingsley Amis - and free speech - against some of the top women in American publishing. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less